data.description: This beautiful, well maintained one-story home is conveniently located just off of IH35 and Eisenhauer. This location gives you easy access to just about anything and everything on the northeast of San Antonio. Perfect for first time home buyers, featuring 3 bedrooms and 1 bath with an open floor plan. The kitchen is equipped with a new stainless steel dishwasher, refrigerator and granite countertops. New flooring and paint throughout the home. Home is set up with owned security system and SOLAR PANELS that will save the new owner on electricity. The backyard is HUGE with shed that will remain. Schedule your private tour today and fall in love with this beautiful home.    .::PREFERRED LENDER INCENTIVES::.
